{"data":{"title":"product owner","date":"2017-10-23T09:30:00.000Z","permalink":"/entry/2017/10/23/product-owner/","_entry":"posts/2017-10-23-product-owner/index.md","page":"post","name":"index","category":"2017-10-23-product-owner","url":"/entry/2017/10/23/product-owner/"},"content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"個人的な意見"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完成した後に後出しジャンケンで要件を伝えるのは悪"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"変更はすればいい。「出せない」を言うのは何時何時であれ遅いので、言いたいやつは目を凝らす"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"そもそも、出せる・出せないを判断する人間はプロダクトから目を離すべきではない"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"決定を譲渡できないのであれば人の3倍目を凝らして稼働しろ"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"決められない人間はオーナーではない"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"外からの要件を100とする行為も同義"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"言った言わなかった論は不毛"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"誰も報われない"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"raw":"# 個人的な意見\n\n1. 完成した後に後出しジャンケンで要件を伝えるのは悪\n1. 変更はすればいい。「出せない」を言うのは何時何時であれ遅いので、言いたいやつは目を凝らす\n1. そもそも、出せる・出せないを判断する人間はプロダクトから目を離すべきではない\n1. 決定を譲渡できないのであれば人の3倍目を凝らして稼働しろ\n    1. 決められない人間はオーナーではない\n    1. 外からの要件を100とする行為も同義\n1. 言った言わなかった論は不毛\n    1. 誰も報われない\n"}